snippet.title: Touhou 5: Mystic Square - Stage 3 (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
A dark city within Hell

Now the difficulty amps up a bit with now even the basic enemies shooting at you. However in almost all cases the bullets are aimed at you so use that information to make sure you don't get cornered.

Alice is also much tougher, for a stage 3 boss right after the simplicity of stage 2 the difficulty curve jumps way up. The problem isn't necessarily Alice's attacks per say but her two dolls that are constantly hovering about. They will randomly attack at what seems to be the most inopportune moments a lot of times making it so you have to figure out how to dodge Alice's and both of her dolls attacks at the same time.

Difficulty - Normal
Character - The Evil Spirit - Mima
Stage 3 - Makai ~ Devil's World 
BGM - Romantic Children 
Boss - Girl of Death: Alice
BGM - Plastic Mind

Translation's courtesy of the Touhou wiki
